{"type":"message","id":"f65faead","parentId":"41d5c08e","timestamp":"2026-03-19T03:48:52.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user hasn't authorized the Feishu OAuth yet. I need to inform the user that authorization is required for these features to work.","thinkingSignature":"9e60e00314422e0024b43d35879d9e2e70ed62cfc1f643a8d8c715fedf42224f"},{"type":"text","text":"**⚠️ 需要授权**\n\n您好，Sir！Otter 需要获得飞书授权才能查看您的日历和任务。\n\n请完成飞书 OAuth 授权后，我就能为您展示：\n- 📅 今日日程安排\n- ✅ 待办事项清单\n- 📋 今日行程概览\n\n授权完成后，请告诉我一声，Otter 会立即为您检查！"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":420,"output":106,"cacheRead":36895,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37421,"cost":{"input":0.000126,"output":0.0001272,"cacheRead":0.00110685,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0013600499999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773892128900}}
